          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, top, tail and slice the <strong>radishes </strong>(as finely as you can)</p><p>Slice the <strong>cucumber</strong> finely</p><p>Cut the <strong>sugar snap peas</strong> in half lengthways</p>",
