    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>grated garlic</strong> (don't like raw garlic? Use half!) with the<strong> </strong>juice of 1/2<span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lime</strong>, the <strong>tamari soy sauce </strong>and<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in a large bowl</p><p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>chilli & lime dressing</strong></p>",
