      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>brown rice</strong>, <strong>sliced radishes</strong>,<strong> sliced cucumber</strong> and <strong>chopped sugar snap peas</strong> to the bowl with the chilli & lime dressing</p><p>Give everything a gentle mix up – this is your <strong>crunchy</strong> <strong>brown rice salad</strong></p>",
